<br>
&lt;shrugs&gt; <br>
<br>
It does bug me that so many folks are greedy on FV, since this is in large part why I'm downgrading my activities on Povar. <br>
<br>
A simple way to know if your missing the &quot;point&quot; of EQ is how you answer the following question.<br>
<br>
Which is a better warrior, a level 60 with planar gear and primal weapons, or a level 5 with a tarnished weapon and full rawhide/cloth?<br>
<br>
The answer, of course, is neither warrior is better than the other. Many folks, caught up in the greed race, will answer that the level 60 is better.<br>
<br>
I've lead many upper mid level kills - Phinny, Talendor, Ragefire, Nagafen, Vox etc. And folks, there ain't a durn thing different about killing them than about killing Muglewump in the Warrens. Get that, and enjoy EQ.<br>
