<br>
Thank you for posting this infraction.  It is a good warning to everyone, not just that we should keep an eye out for a said person (though issue is now resolved), but also to remind everyone the consequences of not listening to and following the rules of your group/raid leader.<br>
<br>
Such replies to this original post (mine included) are also good to show the rest of us, whom among the FV community are the ones who are not afraid to publicly judge the rest of us....Some of whom have high standards and expect everyone else to live up to their standards, or some who want everyone else to know of their high standards (so perhaps we will think more highly of them), and then others who fall into all OR none of the already mentioned categories, so on and so forth.<br>
<br>
My comments are not intended to lessen validity of the charge in this conflict.  Bringing the perpetrator to public attention and scrutiny was probably the best thing to do to bring about timely and just resolution to this conflict.<br>
<br>
/salute<br>
